hopobject.body: Cool site goodluck :) www.moh.ehealth.go.tz Life for the West Monroe Robertsons, America's most famous family, has become an exciting, exhausting, blur. They manage a four-day-a-week filming schedule for "Duck Dynasty," 500 daily requests for appearances, book tours for three bestsellers, a Christmas album, art projects and a Christian Caribbean cruise. Oh, and they still have to manage the multimillion Duck Commander company that patriarch Phil Robertson founded to start it all.
